text: Paris Passlib’: Paris’s official and 100% customizable city pass
With the Paris Passlib’, enjoy Paris as you go, the way you want to!
Paris Passlib’ - the official Paris city pass

emphasized_text_contents: official pass of the Paris Tourist Office

text: Put together your very own sightseeing programme for your stay in Paris with the Paris Passlib’, the official pass of the Paris Tourist Office!

emphasized_text_contents: great way to make the most of Paris

text: Available in 5 versions, it is a great way to make the most of Paris, with a wide selection of visits and attractions to choose from!

This fully digital pass can be instantly activated and used. All you have to do is download the Paris Passlib’ app to your smartphone and either enter the number on your pass or scan the QR code you received when your purchase was confirmed.

emphasized_text_contents: for a single stay or for several

text: Whether you use it for a single stay or for several, the Paris Passlib’ guarantees you a maximum of freedom!
